      "role": "user",
      "content": "the walk sounds a bit much a bit dizzy too... you sure it's just anxiety? i've heard sometimes long flights can cause issues with blood clots or something. i don't want to go to a hospital in a foreign country if i don't have to, it seems like overkill if it's just stress.",
